{"tid":1113723,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拿樸迪係一個壞左既人","createTime":"2019-04-18T05:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T05:47:21.000Z","uid":34934,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4856c753b0da8c5a323eb99bb0c817a56a97ed47","tid":1113723,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T05:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得自己好丟臉 我嘔心 好陌生<br />\n我有深刻既反思自己點解去犯呢個錯誤<br />\n今造成輸波<br />\n我覺得係承擔責任果到 <br />\n我會分兩個部分<br />\n第一個部分<br />\n我會暫停我所有係足球嘅工作<br />\n直至到穩到一個真正的自己<br />\n重新去檢視自己<br />\n第二個部分係係我個心靈上面<br />\n我覺得我自己不知所謂<br />\n因為我既行為 我既錯誤<br />\n令我身邊所有球迷<br />\n承受咁樣既壓力同埋痛苦<br />\n我希望係黎緊既日子裡<br />\n將所有比我整痛整傷既人<br />\n都可以好好。。。<br />\n出局開令我反思既一點<br />\n我最錯既地方係冇去守魚興敏<br />\n我最後同所有愛我既人講一句對唔住<br />\n對唔住令你地難堪<br />\n我做錯咗 <br />\n同埋對唔住曼城<br />\n我唔知點樣走我自己既路啊<br />\n我呢一刻 <br />\n係冇咗靈魂既<br />\n我係一個壞咗既球員<br />\n期望大家可以比時間我穩返我自己<br />\n最後我同大家講一聲對唔住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aff4e3dfdfcd1f5b14b4ac0ffa8a8fb9c5077bb","tid":1113723,"uid":1696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T05:33:29.000Z","msg":"走啦垃圾拿"},{"pid":"e85703c0732a9267bede2cf3c5baffae1adcad1b","tid":1113723,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4856c753b0da8c5a323eb99bb0c817a56a97ed47","tid":1113723,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T05:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得自己好丟臉 我嘔心 好陌生<br />\n我有深刻既反思自己點解去犯呢個錯誤<br />\n今造成輸波<br />\n我